<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Get 36 Free Smoothie Recipes - Daily Smoothies</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Download 36 delicious, healthy smoothie recipes FREE. Includes 3-day detox plan, 21-day meal plan, and shopping lists.">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --primary: #FF6B6B;
      --secondary: #4ECDC4;
      --dark: #2D3142;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--dark);
      background: var(--light);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 3rem;
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .benefits {
      background: var(--light);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .benefits ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .benefits li {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }

    .benefits li::before {
      content: "✅";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }

    .form-container {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: 2px solid var(--light);
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--secondary);
    }

    .submit-button {
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .submit-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .trust-badges {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--light);
    }

    .trust-badges p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .guarantee {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, var(--primary) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .guarantee h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        margin: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>🍓 Get Your Free Smoothie Recipes!</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Enter your email below and get instant access to all 36 recipes + meal plans</p>

    <div class="benefits">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>36 Complete Smoothie Recipes</strong> - Ingredients, instructions, nutrition info</li>
        <li><strong>3-Day Detox Plan</strong> - Optional kickstart to reset your body</li>
        <li><strong>21-Day Rapid Fat Loss Plan</strong> - Daily meal schedule included</li>
        <li><strong>Weekly Shopping Lists</strong> - Print and go grocery shopping</li>
        <li><strong>Pro Blending Tips</strong> - Get perfect smoothies every time</li>
        <li><strong>Instant PDF Download</strong> - Get it in your inbox in 2 minutes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="form-container">
      <!-- TODO: Replace with actual MailerLite form embed -->
      <form id="smoothie-form" action="https://assets.mailerlite.com/jsonp/XXXXX/forms/XXXXX/subscribe" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email Address:</label>
          <input 
            type="email" 
            id="email" 
            name="fields[email]" 
            placeholder="your@email.com" 
            required
          />
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">First Name (optional):</label>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="name" 
            name="fields[name]" 
            placeholder="Your first name"
          />
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="submit-button">
          Send Me The Free Recipes! 🎉
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="guarantee">
      <h3>💯 100% Free. No Credit Card Required.</h3>
      <p>I'll send you the PDF immediately. No spam, ever. Unsubscribe anytime with one click.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-badges">
      <p>🔒 Your email is safe. I hate spam as much as you do.</p>
      <p>📧 20,000+ people have downloaded these recipes</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // TODO: Add MailerLite form handling
    document.getElementById('smoothie-form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      alert('Form will be connected to MailerLite. Integration coming soon!');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
